Coding Conventions:

    identation: 4 spaces

    ClassName

    functionName

    methods:
        CName_methodName
          ^
          +-- abbreviation of class name

    if ( expression ) {
        command1();
        command();
    } else {
        command();      <-  use brackets even if this is just one command
    }

    * by calling format.sh all code will be formatted with current coding conventions
    (requires astyle)



